  "verses": [
    {
      "n": 20,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Patargi mannu Dweh- li/ un iſglabb manni/ ne leež\nmann Rauna tapt/ jo es patau-\nhs us tew.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 21,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Sirđs-Skaidriba un\naſniba lai manni patarga/ jo\ngaidu us tew.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 22,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Ak Deews! ispesti Isra-\nn no wiſſahm winna Beh-\nahin.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 1,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Ta XXVI. Dseefma.\nweena Luhgſchana Dahwida/ eekſch ka wiſch\npirmis Deewu luhds/ lai tas winnu glahbj\nprett teem Wajatajeem/ eekſch weenas taiſ-\nnas Leetas/ jo wiſch efu nenoseedsigs/ un\nzerrejus us winnu :1/2. Pehz apjohlahs\nwiſch par to pateikt: 12.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 2,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Weena Dahwida Dseefma.\nKUNGS/ spreed man\nTeefu/ jo es staigaju\nWeekſch mannas Sirđs-\nskaidribas/ un pataujobs us\nKUNGS/ es ne ſchaubſchohs.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 3,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Pahrbaudi mannis\nUNGS/ un pahrmanni man-\n/ iſluhko mannas Jhktis un\nannu Sirđi.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 4,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Jo tawa Schehlastiba irr\nreekſch mannahin Azzim/ un es\naigaju eekſch tawas Pateeſibas.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 5,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Es ne febschohs pee nelee-\nheem Laudim/ un ar Wilti-\nem es ne tinnohs.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 6,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Es eenihstu to Laundarri-\nju Draudsi/ un pee teem Bes-\netwigeem es ne febſchu.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 7,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Es masgaju jawas Roh-\ns eekſch Nenoseedsibas/ un et-\nu KUNGS fahrt tawu Altari.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 7,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Ka es dsirdeht leeku to\nTeikſchanas Balsi/ un fluddi-\nnaju wiſſus tawus Brihnunus.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 8,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "KUNGS/ es mihleju to\nMahjas-Weetu tawa Namna/\nun tawas Gohdibas Telts\nWeetu.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 9,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Ne aisrauji mannu Dweh-\nfeli ar teem Grehzineekeem/ nedg\nmannu Dshwitbu ar teem Affi-\nnu Laudim.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 10,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Kas ar wiltigahm Doh-\nmahm tinnahs/ un nem lab-\npraht Dahwanas.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 11,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Bet es staigaju eekſch ta-\nwas Sirđs-Skaidribas/ atpesti\nmanni/ un apschehlojees pahr\nmannim.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 12,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Manna Kahja stahw us\nlihdseuu Zełtu/ es teikſchu to\nKUNGU eekſch tahm Draudsi-\nbahm.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 1,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Ta XXVII. Dseefma.\nIrr weena Luhgſchanas un Eepreeginaschanas\nDseefma/ tapehz ka Deews muhsu Gai-\nſchums un muhsu Pestisçhana/ mums ne irr\njabihſtahs: 1/ etc. Tomehr buhs mums\nwinnu ſirdigi peesaukt/ ka wiſch muhs pee\niſtas Deewa Kalpoſchanas usturreht: 4.\nMuhsu Luhgſchanu paklausijht/un prett wiſ-\nfeem Eenaidneekem glabbaht gribbetu: 6/rc.\nWeena Dahwida Dseefma.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 1,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "As KUNGS irr mans\nGaitchums un manna\nPestisçhana/ preekſch ka\nbij mann bihtees? tas KUNGS\nirr mannas Dshwitbas Stip-\nrums/ preekſch ka bij mann bat-\nlotees?\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 2,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Kad tee Launee/ manni\nPrettineeki un Eenaidneeki us\nman lauschahs/ mannu Meeſu\nOaaaaa ehſt/\n"
    }
  ],
